## Supporting Recurring Rivals

These two characters provide external pressure without expanding the playable cast.

### Petra Vale, Claims Registrar

- human face of salvage law
- smart, underpaid, dangerous
- can be bribed, outmaneuvered, or eventually convinced
- represents "the system can digest dissent and invoice it"

### Captain Orin Bale, Helix Recovery Lead

- corporate rival scavenger captain
- professional, ruthless, not cartoonishly evil
- his crew are treated better than yours because their contracts are just hidden better
- represents the future where the player wins materially but becomes part of the machine

